SUMMARY:Rising Artisans Kids Fine Art Classes Ages 9+
DTSTAMP:20260307T061513Z
DTSTART:20260307T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Under the guidance of local teaching artist Athena Louscher\, y
	our young artist explores their creativity with a variety of materials\, a
	nd learns to build their own projects and skills. The student projects and
	 concepts taught build and grow\, with more complexity as grades increase\
	, up to support for high schoolers looking to build portfolios and/or expl
	oring higher-education art programs.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/event
