BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:0Sp8ptDEr9u_b0rCyk0m6
SUMMARY:Eastside Community School Open House
DTSTAMP:20260307T061513Z
DTSTART:20260307T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Step inside Eastside Community School and experience the vibran
	t world of a Waldorf-inspired education. From Preschool through Grade 8\, 
	students learn through a rich balance of academics\, artistic expression\,
	 handwork\, and movement\, all designed to support curiosity\, confidence\
	, and joy in learning. At our All School Open House\, you'll: Tour our be
	autiful Issaquah campus Experience classrooms through the eyes of a stude
	nt Participate in experiential activities Meet our talented\, caring fac
	ulty Learn about our admissions process Whether you're new to Waldorf or 
	simply curious\, we invite you to see how our approach meets the needs of 
	children in today's world. We hope to see you there! Saturday\, March 7th\
	, 9 - 11:30 am 5025 Issaquah-Pine Lake Rd SE\, Issaquah WA 98029 RSVP 425-
	598-2914 EASTSIDE COMMUNITY SCHOOL -Learning Rooted in Experience\, Ready 
	for Life\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/eastside-communi
	ty-school-open-house/18265086/2026-03-07T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/eastside-community-school
	-open-house/18265086/2026-03-07T00
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H30M
END:VEVENT
